sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film .
        ?uri dbo:director res:Akira_Kurosawa .
      { ?uri dbo:releaseDate ?x . } 
      UNION 
      { ?uri dbp:released ?x . }
        res:Rashomon dbo:releaseDate ?y .
        FILTER (?y > ?x)
}

languageToQuestion.en: Which movies did Kurosawa direct after Rashomon?
languageToQuestion.de: Welche Filme hat Kurosawa nach Rashomon gedreht?
languageToQuestion.es: ¿Qué películas ha rodado Kurosawa después de Rashomon?
languageToQuestion.it: Che film ha diretto Kurosawa dopo Rashomon?
languageToQuestion.fr: Quels films ont été realisés par Kurosawa après Rashomon?
languageToQuestion.nl: Welke films heeft Kurosawa geregisseerd na Rashomon?
languageToQuestion.ro: Ce filme a regizat Kurosawa după Rashomon?

sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> 
ASK 
WHERE { 
        <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_William,_Duke_of_Cambridge> dbp:mother ?x . 
        <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Harry_of_Wales> dbp:mother ?y . 
        FILTER (?x = ?y) 
}

sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {
         ?uri rdf:type dbo:Person .
         ?uri dbo:office '1st President of the United States'@en .
}

}
